<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ROMA MODA STYLE - تطبيق الأحذية والحقائب الفاخرة</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A961 0%, #E6D5B8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        
        .status {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-right: 5px solid #C9A961;
        }
        
        .status h2 {
            color: #C9A961;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }
        
        .status p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .feature {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2);
        }
        
        .feature h3 {
            color: #C9A961;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.4em;
        }
        
        .feature p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        .products-preview {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .products-preview h2 {
            color: #C9A961;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }
        
        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .product-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9f9f9 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #E6D5B8;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .product-card:hover {
            border-color: #C9A961;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2);
        }
        
        .product-card h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .product-price {
            color: #C9A961;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .product-category {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A961 0%, #B8932F 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B8932F 0%, #A0800B 100%);
        }
        
        .coming-soon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E1 0%, #FFE082 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #C9A961;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .coming-soon h3 {
            color: #C9A961;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        footer p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            color: #C9A961;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .products-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🌟 ROMA MODA STYLE 🌟</h1>
            <p>تطبيق الأحذية والحقائب الفاخرة للنساء</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="coming-soon">
            <h3>🚀 قريباً جداً!</h3>
            <p>نحن نعمل على إطلاق تطبيق ROMA MODA STYLE الفاخر!</p>
